    {
      "id": "ctcWtvKwqHEZMccIioQLa",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2352.6616821289062,
      "y": 43.5302734375,
      "width": 749.5594482421875,
      "height": 575,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "at",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 265562130,
      "version": 11,
      "versionNonce": 1038398734,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782995880322,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "InlineSkipList 表级模拟布局\n\nLevel 3\n+--------+      +--------+                                  +--------+\n| Head   | ---> | key=A  | --------------------------------> | key=Z  |\n+--------+      +--------+                                  +--------+\n\nLevel 2\n+--------+      +--------+              +--------+           +--------+\n| Head   | ---> | key=A  | -----------> | key=H  | --------> | key=Z  |\n+--------+      +--------+              +--------+           +--------+\n\nLevel 1\n+--------+      +--------+    +--------+    +--------+       +--------+\n| Head   | ---> | key=A  | -> | key=D  | -> | key=H  | ----> | key=Z  |\n+--------+      +--------+    +--------+    +--------+       +--------+\n\nLevel 0\n+--------+      +--------+    +--------+    +--------+    +--------+    +--------+\n| Head   | ---> | key=A  | -> | key=B  | -> | key=D  | -> | key=H  | -> | key=Z  |\n+--------+      +--------+    +--------+    +--------+    +--------+    +--------+\n\n底层 `Level 0` 串起全部节点；高层只保留一部分节点，作为稀疏索引。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "InlineSkipList 表级模拟布局\n\nLevel 3\n+--------+      +--------+                                  +--------+\n| Head   | ---> | key=A  | --------------------------------> | key=Z  |\n+--------+      +--------+                                  +--------+\n\nLevel 2\n+--------+      +--------+              +--------+           +--------+\n| Head   | ---> | key=A  | -----------> | key=H  | --------> | key=Z  |\n+--------+      +--------+              +--------+           +--------+\n\nLevel 1\n+--------+      +--------+    +--------+    +--------+       +--------+\n| Head   | ---> | key=A  | -> | key=D  | -> | key=H  | ----> | key=Z  |\n+--------+      +--------+    +--------+    +--------+       +--------+\n\nLevel 0\n+--------+      +--------+    +--------+    +--------+    +--------+    +--------+\n| Head   | ---> | key=A  | -> | key=B  | -> | key=D  | -> | key=H  | -> | key=Z  |\n+--------+      +--------+    +--------+    +--------+    +--------+    +--------+\n\n底层 `Level 0` 串起全部节点；高层只保留一部分节点，作为稀疏索引。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "d3sxtVtesVD-R8ubduYvC",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2272.6710815429688,
      "y": 162.2802734375,
      "width": 793.3394775390625,
      "height": 625,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "au",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 489971282,
      "version": 47,
      "versionNonce": 2059697358,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782997259326,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "InlineSkipList 表级模拟布局\n\nLevel 3\n+--------+      +--------+                                                      +--------+\n| Head   | ---> | key=A  | ----------------------------------------------->     | key=Z  |\n+--------+      +--------+                                                      +--------+\n\nLevel 2\n+--------+      +--------+                                      +--------+      +--------+\n| Head   | ---> | key=A  | -----------------------------------> | key=H  | ---> | key=Z  |\n+--------+      +--------+                                      +--------+      +--------+\n\nLevel 1\n+--------+      +--------+                      +--------+      +--------+      +--------+\n| Head   | ---> | key=A  | ------------------>  | key=D  | ---> | key=H  | ---> | key=Z\n|\n+--------+      +--------+                      +--------+      +--------+      +--------+\n\nLevel 0\n+--------+      +--------+      +--------+      +--------+      +--------+      +--------+\n| Head   | ---> | key=A  | ---> | key=B  | ---> | key=D  | ---> | key=H  | ---> | key=Z\n|\n+--------+      +--------+      +--------+      +--------+      +--------+      +--------+\n\n底层 `Level 0` 串起全部节点；高层只保留一部分节点，作为稀疏索引。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "InlineSkipList 表级模拟布局\n\nLevel 3\n+--------+      +--------+                                                      +--------+\n| Head   | ---> | key=A  | ----------------------------------------------->     | key=Z  |\n+--------+      +--------+                                                      +--------+\n\nLevel 2\n+--------+      +--------+                                      +--------+      +--------+\n| Head   | ---> | key=A  | -----------------------------------> | key=H  | ---> | key=Z  |\n+--------+      +--------+                                      +--------+      +--------+\n\nLevel 1\n+--------+      +--------+                      +--------+      +--------+      +--------+\n| Head   | ---> | key=A  | ------------------>  | key=D  | ---> | key=H  | ---> | key=Z  |\n+--------+      +--------+                      +--------+      +--------+      +--------+\n\nLevel 0\n+--------+      +--------+      +--------+      +--------+      +--------+      +--------+\n| Head   | ---> | key=A  | ---> | key=B  | ---> | key=D  | ---> | key=H  | ---> | key=Z  |\n+--------+      +--------+      +--------+      +--------+      +--------+      +--------+\n\n底层 `Level 0` 串起全部节点；高层只保留一部分节点，作为稀疏索引。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "slPeR5aUdny4jkzdB3Q28",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2849.6875,
