      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782997448824,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "InlineSkipList node 的直观布局\n\nhigher-level next pointers\n┌───────────────┐\n│ next[level n] │\n│ ...           │\n│ next[level 1] │\n├───────────────┤\n│ Node metadata │\n├───────────────┤\n│ key bytes     │  <- MemTable entry bytes 紧跟 Node\n└───────────────┘",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "InlineSkipList node 的直观布局\n\nhigher-level next pointers\n┌───────────────┐\n│ next[level n] │\n│ ...           │\n│ next[level 1] │\n├───────────────┤\n│ Node metadata │\n├───────────────┤\n│ key bytes     │  <- MemTable entry bytes 紧跟 Node\n└───────────────┘",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
