      "text": "InlineSkipList 表级模拟布局\n\nLevel 3\n+--------+      +--------+                                                            +--------+\n| Head   | ---> | key=A  | ----------------------------------------------------->  | key=Z |\n+--------+      +--------+                                                            +--------+\n\nLevel 2\n+--------+      +--------+                                           +--------+      +--------+\n| Head   | ---> | key=A  | ------------------------------------>  | key=H  | ---> | key=Z |\n+--------+      +--------+                                          +--------+       +--------+\n\nLevel 1\n+--------+      +--------+                       +--------+        +--------+      +--------+\n| Head   | ---> | key=A | ------------------>  | key=D | --->  | key=H | ---> | key=Z |\n+--------+      +--------+                       +--------+        +--------+      +--------+\n\nLevel 0\n+--------+      +--------+       +--------+      +--------+      +--------+       +--------+\n| Head   | ---> | key=A  | ---> | key=B | --->| key=D | ---> | key=H  | ---> | key=Z  |\n+--------+      +--------+       +--------+      +--------+      +--------+       +--------+",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "InlineSkipList 表级模拟布局\n\nLevel 3\n+--------+      +--------+                                                            +--------+\n| Head   | ---> | key=A  | ----------------------------------------------------->  | key=Z |\n+--------+      +--------+                                                            +--------+\n\nLevel 2\n+--------+      +--------+                                           +--------+      +--------+\n| Head   | ---> | key=A  | ------------------------------------>  | key=H  | ---> | key=Z |\n+--------+      +--------+                                          +--------+       +--------+\n\nLevel 1\n+--------+      +--------+                       +--------+        +--------+      +--------+\n| Head   | ---> | key=A | ------------------>  | key=D | --->  | key=H | ---> | key=Z |\n+--------+      +--------+                       +--------+        +--------+      +--------+\n\nLevel 0\n+--------+      +--------+       +--------+      +--------+      +--------+       +--------+\n| Head   | ---> | key=A  | ---> | key=B | --->| key=D | ---> | key=H  | ---> | key=Z  |\n+--------+      +--------+       +--------+      +--------+      +--------+       +--------+",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
