      "locked": false,
      "text": "InlineSkipList node 的直观布局\n+-------------------+ \n| next[level n]    | <- higher-level next pointers\n| ...                 |\n| next[level 1]    |\n+-------------------+ \n| Node metadata |\n+-------------------+ \n| key bytes        |  <- MemTable entry bytes 紧跟 Node\n+-------------------+",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "InlineSkipList node 的直观布局\n+-------------------+ \n| next[level n]    | <- higher-level next pointers\n| ...                 |\n| next[level 1]    |\n+-------------------+ \n| Node metadata |\n+-------------------+ \n| key bytes        |  <- MemTable entry bytes 紧跟 Node\n+-------------------+",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "OxMnPhXbwityLpUou4em2",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1488.131352015904,
      "y": -6.196010044643003,
      "width": 449.1796875,
      "height": 500,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
