      "updated": 1783080647259,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "`VersionEdit` \n+------------------------+---------------------------------+\n| Tag                    | Payload                        |\n+------------------------+---------------------------------+\n| comparator           | comparator name              |\n| log_number           | current WAL number           |\n| next_file_number    | next allocatable file number |\n| deleted_file          | which SST is obsolete       |\n| new_file               | new SST metadata           |\n| column_family_add  | new CF metadata             |\n| wal_addition         | tracked WAL metadata       |\n| ...                      | ...                                |\n+------------------------+---------------------------------+",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "`VersionEdit` \n+------------------------+---------------------------------+\n| Tag                    | Payload                        |\n+------------------------+---------------------------------+\n| comparator           | comparator name              |\n| log_number           | current WAL number           |\n| next_file_number    | next allocatable file number |\n| deleted_file          | which SST is obsolete       |\n| new_file               | new SST metadata           |\n| column_family_add  | new CF metadata             |\n| wal_addition         | tracked WAL metadata       |\n| ...                      | ...                                |\n+------------------------+---------------------------------+",
